claim.claim-text:
18. A sprinkling system comprising: 
a) an electrical non-priming submersible pump; 
b) a control panel in communication with said pump for regulating liquid flow; 
c) a first means for connecting the pump to the control panel; 
d) a header pipe section 
e) a second means for connecting said control panel to said header pipe section; 
f) at least one zone pipe section connected to said header pipe section; and 
g) at least one sprinkler head interposed within the at least one zone pipe section for applying water to a desired location.
